{"tid":2462030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「安心出行」紀錄會被上傳至衞生署，將保存最少 7 年及可轉交其他部門","createTime":"2021-03-25T17:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T20:37:40.000Z","uid":108814,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de613ea355b01e0fae8b295f51967a2f76f228ae","tid":2462030,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"香港政府推出的「安心出行」應用程式一直被指會收集用戶個人資料，政府就不斷強調資料只會加密存放在用戶手機內，並在 31 天後自動刪除，不過近日就有人在「安心出行」網頁的個人資料收集聲明頁面中，發現寫有確診個案的紀錄將保存最少 7 年，更可能會把提供的資料提供予其他獲授權部門、組織或人士，與之前所說的內容不同。<br />\n<br />\n根據「安心出行」網頁中的個人資料收集聲明頁面，寫有「如屬確診個案，經「安心出行」手機應用上傳至衞生署的出行記錄將保存最少 7 年。」顯示出行紀錄有機會上傳給衞生署，與政府強調的資料只會存放在手機、不會備存不同。而且網頁中更表示「在有需要時，在有關條例及／或其附屬法例下，為了計劃及所有相關的用途，資科辦可能會把你提供的資料提供予其他獲授權部門／組織／人士，包括衞生署、醫院管理局及負責流行病學調查和接觸追蹤工作的執法人員。」即上傳了的紀錄可隨時轉交給其他部門使用，用家提供了資料之後，不會知道資料被轉交至什麼人，以及用作什麼用途，令人不安。<br />\n<br />\n港共正苦唔扮野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接借防疫全面監控"},{"pid":"857d3cec123b185009c34cf0216ad5c357dc44a3","tid":2462030,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc3c190877ba4dc4475746e5a908966652afa1d","tid":2462030,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9d1d6e1e666b43026b672665632ad305c9733e","tid":2462030,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbaf079ff93a4f0f524435ab1b48e4d3275e6e0","tid":2462030,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:49:07.000Z","msg":"係愈來愈多人走去scan<br />\n晚餐求其食個越南河粉啲人都scan左先叫野食<br />\n<br />\n暫時見廢老年齡三十零都有"},{"pid":"e7c8f4cfadf0fc15fd730e15939c7c0a0e3a00cc","tid":2462030,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:35:48.000Z","msg":"確診個案的紀錄將保存最少 7 年<br />\n<br />\n隻菌過左7年仲周圍傳?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939ad93849ed598c0423d4af64280fd8979e1fb9","tid":2462030,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7c8f4cfadf0fc15fd730e15939c7c0a0e3a00cc","tid":2462030,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:35:48.000Z","msg":"確診個案的紀錄將保存最少 7 年<br />\n<br />\n隻菌過左7年仲周圍傳?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"改正<br />\n<br />\n隻菌傳播期7年?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85be68c6bcb1144bc1cf218e22a49c6c7b2776f1","tid":2462030,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4cbaa175c4f1000974a32948122a8c3654a3a0","tid":2462030,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939ad93849ed598c0423d4af64280fd8979e1fb9","tid":2462030,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7c8f4cfadf0fc15fd730e15939c7c0a0e3a00cc","tid":2462030,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:35:48.000Z","msg":"確診個案的紀錄將保存最少 7 年<br />\n<br />\n隻菌